00:02:02.520 --> 00:02:05.940 align:middle line:90%
>> Noah, what about you?

00:02:05.940 --> 00:02:08.572 align:middle line:10%
>> The one example that
sticks out in my mind is,

00:02:08.572 --> 00:02:10.530 align:middle line:10%
although there was lots
of meditation practice,

00:02:10.530 --> 00:02:12.550 align:middle line:10%
spiritual practice
going on around,

00:02:12.550 --> 00:02:15.660 align:middle line:10%
was never really
imposed or offered.

00:02:15.660 --> 00:02:19.470 align:middle line:10%
