meditate as a young person.

00:02:19.470 --> 00:02:22.500 align:middle line:84%
But certainly, those seeds
were sown in my consciousness

00:02:22.500 --> 00:02:25.110 align:middle line:90%
just from being around it.

00:02:25.110 --> 00:02:27.330 align:middle line:84%
One example is I can remember
burning myself pretty

00:02:27.330 --> 00:02:30.360 align:middle line:84%
bad on a heater when I was
about four or five years old,

00:02:30.360 --> 00:02:31.830 align:middle line:90%
about that same age.

00:02:31.830 --> 00:02:34.680 align:middle line:84%
And my instant reaction, I
think people's instant reaction

00:02:34.680 --> 00:02:37.920 align:middle line:84%
is to tighten and maybe
get angry at the pain,

00:02:37.920 --> 00:02:39.180 align:middle line:90%
out of the fear.

00:02:39.180 --> 00:02:40.980 align:middle line:84%
And my father's
instruction was to really

00:02:40.980 --> 00:02:44.250 align:middle line:84%
soften to it, to send
love to the pain,

00:02:44.250 --> 00:02:46.868 align:middle line:84%
to send softness
into the sensation,

00:02:46.868 --> 00:02:48.660 align:middle line:84%
and to watch the
sensation moment to moment

00:02:48.660 --> 00:02:52.830 align:middle line:84%
as it passes, rather than
just screaming and sending

00:02:52.830 --> 00:02:58.570 align:middle line:84%
the hatred into, damn you,
my body that hurt so badly.

00:02:58.570 --> 00:03:00.900 align:middle line:84%
And so then throughout my
life, I had that conditioning

00:03:00.900 --> 00:03:04.770 align:middle line:84%
of when I stubbed my toe,
rather than my instant reaction

00:03:04.770 --> 00:03:07.360 align:middle line:84%
might be to tighten and
to send anger to it,

00:03:07.360 --> 00:03:11.460 align:middle line:84%
but then to also remember
how softening dissipates

00:03:11.460 --> 00:03:13.150 align:middle line:90%
the pain much more quickly.

00:03:13.150 --> 00:03:16.650 align:middle line:84%
So things like that that weren't
like, this is meditation,

00:03:16.650 --> 00:03:20.370 align:middle line:84%
but certainly that came out
of the meditative tradition.

00:03:20.370 --> 00:03:21.630 align:middle line:90%
>> Ocean.

00:03:21.630 --> 00:03:24.750 align:middle line:10%
>> Well, my mom and dad
