economically, but feeling rich

00:03:38.910 --> 00:03:41.175 align:middle line:84%
because I had beautiful
forest to enjoy.

00:03:41.175 --> 00:03:43.600 align:middle line:90%
I had clean water and clean air.

00:03:43.600 --> 00:03:45.540 align:middle line:90%
I had time with my mom and dad.

00:03:45.540 --> 00:03:49.230 align:middle line:84%
And they were in a very
deep meditative space.

00:03:49.230 --> 00:03:51.280 align:middle line:84%
They grew almost
all their own food.

00:03:51.280 --> 00:03:53.700 align:middle line:84%
They lived on less
than $500 a year.

00:03:53.700 --> 00:03:58.440 align:middle line:84%
And their whole life revolved
around meditation and yoga

00:03:58.440 --> 00:04:02.760 align:middle line:84%
and spiritual practice and
connection with the earth.

00:04:02.760 --> 00:04:06.780 align:middle line:84%
And as I was a little older, we
wound up moving to California.

00:04:06.780 --> 00:04:09.210 align:middle line:84%
And I came to see
that not everyone had

00:04:09.210 --> 00:04:13.380 align:middle line:84%
the kind of opportunities
that I had as a youngster.

00:04:13.380 --> 00:04:16.500 align:middle line:84%
And so then my
focus in life became

00:04:16.500 --> 00:04:20.010 align:middle line:84%
working to see to it that
everyone could have things

00:04:20.010 --> 00:04:22.380 align:middle line:84%
like time with their mom and
dad and a safe environment

00:04:22.380 --> 00:04:25.740 align:middle line:84%
to live in and forests to enjoy
because I felt that everyone

00:04:25.740 --> 00:04:27.570 align:middle line:90%
deserved those things.

00:04:27.570 --> 00:04:29.640 align:middle line:84%
And it didn't feel
right that I should

00:04:29.640 --> 00:04:32.610 align:middle line:84%
have those kinds of privileges
where other people grew up

00:04:32.610 --> 00:04:34.860 align:middle line:84%
with gangs and concrete
for their environment.

00:04:34.860 --> 00:04:39.030 align:middle line:84%
And so my whole life really
has revolved since then

00:04:39.030 --> 00:04:41.460 align:middle line:84%
around service and working
to make this world a better

00:04:41.460 --> 00:04:42.877 align:middle line:90%
place for everybody.

00:04:42.877 --> 00:04:45.210 align:middle line:84%
>> How different do you suppose
the world would be today

00:04:45.210 --> 00:04:50.610 align:middle line:84%
environmentally, politically,
financially, I guess, too,

00:04:50.610 --> 00:04:55.830 align:middle line:84%
