00:05:00.930 --> 00:05:02.430 align:middle line:90%
>> Very.

00:05:02.430 --> 00:05:04.900 align:middle line:90%
I mean, I can't say, you know?

00:05:04.900 --> 00:05:05.847 align:middle line:90%
>> You can speculate.

00:05:05.847 --> 00:05:07.930 align:middle line:84%
